<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes_for_Week_5:_3.2_Marginal_Costs">Notes for Week 5: 3.2 Marginal Costs</span></h2>
<p>Because the <strong>Marginal Costs</strong> are defined by the equation: $$MC = \Delta TC / \Delta Q$$ using the hypothetical example adding a column for Marginal Costs.</p>
